    <!-- model selection -->
    <string name="question_mark">question mark</string>
    <string name="ai_model_title">What is an AI model?</string>
    <string name="ai_model_description">An AI model is like a digital brain that has been trained to understand speech and convert it into written text. Different models have different strengths - some are faster, some are more accurate. Choose the one that matches your needs.</string>
    <string name="standard_model_title">German – Moly Optimized</string>
    <string name="standard_model_description">Our own optimized model for the German language – and therefore our recommendation for most users. It delivers highly precise transcriptions and works especially well for clear recordings and everyday conversations. Processing takes a little longer than with the multilingual model – but in return you get significantly more accurate results in German. At around 574 MB, the download size is manageable.</string>
    <string name="optimized_model_title">German – Accurate</string>
    <string name="optimized_model_description">The most powerful model we offer – for those who want to get the absolute best results. Recommended for particularly demanding recordings: lots of background noise, technical jargon, strong accents, or long meetings. At around 1.6 GB, it is considerably larger than the other models, and processing takes noticeably longer. For everyday use, Moly Optimized is the better choice.</string>
    <string name="multilingual_model_title">Multilingual</string>
    <string name="multilingual_model_description">The fastest model – ideal when speed matters most. At around 465 MB, it is the smallest of the available models while supporting over 50 languages. Accuracy is lower than our German models, but perfectly sufficient for quick notes and simple texts. The first choice when speed or multilingual support matters more than maximum precision.</string>
